{"tid":1158896,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"持回鄉證港澳居民內地可享逾30項公共服務　10月起實施","createTime":"2019-05-17T09:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T16:47:28.000Z","uid":135110,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"91d90f33aa4b59ba2f068dc2ac5f851c8896ea0d","tid":1158896,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:52:00.000Z","msg":"國家移民管理局在周四（16日）宣布，自今年10月份起，港澳居民、華僑的出入境證件將成為各類政務服務平台、公共服務平台及互聯網應用程式註冊登記和使用的有效身份證件選項，滿足在各領域要「實名」、「實人」、「實證」的認證需求，為他們持用出入境證件辦理各類社會事務提供更多網上辦理和自助辦理的便利。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，港澳居民、華僑持出入境證件，可在網上或自助辦理社保、工商、稅務、交通等基本公共服務事項；辦理就醫掛號、購買保險、考試報名、共享單車等民生服務事項；辦理銀行、證券、手機開戶和即時註冊開通網絡支付等金融理財事項，涵蓋交通運輸、金融、通訊、教育、醫療、社保、工商、稅務、住宿等9個領域30多項公共民生服務。"},{"pid":"e9c7c01d63dec23615c412ebb83bee2b3583055e","tid":1158896,"uid":135110,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOcKRkm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOcKRkm.png&h=8939982a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2f4816b1f338df5dff04299ff3fa63983db249","tid":1158896,"uid":135110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21613c99930f3f084f9ddbc15db58e8da5f7678","tid":1158896,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T16:33:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: purple;\"></span>"},{"pid":"ef1d005d3f7f887be0e8aa6b717491fd41920189","tid":1158896,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T16:34:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f57a5039ec5542224df25976add2a4fdcb193b4a","tid":1158896,"uid":30384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9c7c01d63dec23615c412ebb83bee2b3583055e","tid":1158896,"uid":135110,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T09:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https